on exitFrame me
  [  0] pusharglistnoret 0 ...................... <>
  [  2] extcall 33 .............................. nextframe()
  [  4] pusharglist 0 ........................... <>
  [  6] thebuiltin 34 ........................... <the frame>
  [  8] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <the frame>
  [ 10] extcall 35 .............................. go(the frame)
  [ 12] ret
end
